How to compile MCE:

Dependencies:
cmake
libdbus
libdbus-glib
glib

Optional dependencies:
osso-systemui
	for systemui support
upower
	to provide battery status for battery low shutdown
libx11
libxi
	to controll the xserver for power management
libcal
libconic

In the repos main directory:
mkdir build
cd build
cmake ..
make
